node.text:
NEWLY RELEASED images by the NTSB of the Transair flight 810 crash, a converted B737-200 freighter, off the coast of Oahu just 11 minutes after takeoff from Honolulu back on July 2 🤨 The cargo plane was on its way to Kahalui in Maui, but experienced trouble with both Pratt & Whitney JT8D engines. The pilots couldn't maintain altitude and had no choice but to ditch the plane. Both pilots survived with serious injuries…

The FAA and the NTSB are investigating the accident.
